markdownRemark.html: This is one of only two golf courses built east of Málaga at the resort town of Rincón de la Victoria, Málaga. Water is a major feature here, used at eleven holes and unforgettable at the 17th where the green is surrounded on all three sides. It offers a good challenge to golfers of all abilities.
